_sText:
BhopCrashEgypt


By FireWavezZ & Rdovydas007



CS:GO map:  http://csgo.gamebanana.com/maps/190574




This is a nearly 100% custom made map based off the legendary Playstation1 game "Crash bandicoot 3: Warped" 
Levels from Tomb time, Tomb wader, Bug lite and Sphynxinator were recreated.

I have to thank tmontana a lot, He has not only helped me to realize this bunny hop map but also gave many ideas and helped anywhere while testing.
Also _unity who is a skilled bunny hop player helped me to test the map whenever needed to make it the way it is now.
And ofcourse all the other people in the credit list who has helped me all the way.

Please do not steal any of it's content without permission,  We spent much time on making everything like models, materials, sounds and particles. Thanks.

I hope you like my first Bhop map and if you do, please let me know! I might just make another one.

Enjoy
